Mjgg3PCopgUwFjj9XkAIcggyNzg2NDk4OXgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "9_1632849153.2997975", "card_id": "Q_488696282", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 107}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "全运会中国象棋大师左文静开局第一手马走「目」而被判负，象棋大师认为系「过于紧张导致」，对此你怎么看？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "陕西全运会正在进行，而在提前进行的中国象棋公开组女子半决赛中却发生了离奇一幕。当时对阵双方是中国象棋大师、曾三次夺得全国智运会冠军的左文静和象棋界的「超级丹」、中国象棋特级大师唐丹。左文静执红先行，结果开局第一手马走「目」而被判负。这也被誉为史上最短的对局，她的对手唐丹一招没出就「躺赢」。象棋特级大师王斌分析：「应该是左文静大师当时比较紧张。这种紧张有可能是因为比赛比较关键，也可能是当时代表团对她的期望很高，毕竟全运会成绩非常重要。」 来源：扬子晚报"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pica.zhimg.com/80/v2-250983662df6ac9bf4d963876443f0c6_1440w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "573 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/488696282"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I3svatbv+1fd/EAMaCDcwODgwODE4IIaetYoGMBg40wZACXIJNDg4Njk2MjgyeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "10_1632849153.3003407", "card_id": "Q_476062325", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 126}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "小动物会觉得自己是毛茸茸的吗？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-9115acc6d6bae00183f14aefd01af5d7_720w.jpg?source=1940ef5c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "483 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/476062325"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I3svatbv+1fd/EAMaCDY4MDcxNzg4IL+mjogGMAs4ugVACnIJNDc2MDYyMzI1eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "11_1632849153.3008285", "card_id": "Q_423533446", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 167}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "为什么钓鱼鱼竿这么讲究，直接拿根硬棍子，咬钩了往上提不就完了，谁能解释一下？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-b986a904287e88182660b6cb9a92923d_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "457 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type":